---
import SectionHeader from "./SectionHeader.astro";
---

<section>
  <SectionHeader id="nindo" label="Nindo" plain="The Ninja Way · About" kanji="道" />
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-prose space-y-4 px-6 pb-8 text-lg leading-relaxed text-paper/90">
    <p>
      I build AI that doesn't just reply — it decides, calls tools, verifies with the web, and
      ships. My focus is agentic systems: multi-agent orchestration, strict tool schemas,
      structured outputs, RAG over private corpora, and multimodal extraction from images
      and audio.
    </p>
    <p>
      I work the full stack so AI features land as real products, not demos — native iOS
      with Swift and CoreLocation, Next.js + FastAPI on the web, Docker around the edges. I
      care about the quiet parts: prompt caching on the cached prefix, graceful tool
      fallbacks, confidence-thresholded review queues, and interfaces that feel intentional.
    </p>
    <p class="text-tan">
      Currently open to roles where AI is the product, not a sidebar.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
